### Overview

Enable video option:
```
video:true
```
To add video into carousel just put `<a class="owl-video" href="_straight URL from YouTube, Vimeo, or vzaar"></a>`.

A tag is not mandatory, it can be any other tag but "owl-video" and href with url link is required.

